    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (

    WHERE @__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [a0].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_2
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[UserName], [t].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[ConcurrencyStamp], [t].[CreationTime], [t].[CreatorUserId], [t].[DeleterUserId], [t].[DeletionTime], [t].[Description], [t].[DisplayName], [t].[IsDefault], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[IsStatic], [t].[LastModificationTime], [t].[LastModifierUserId], [t].[Name], [t].[NormalizedName], [t].[TenantId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreationTime], [t0].[CreatorUserId], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[IsGranted], [t0].[Name], [t0].[TenantId], [t0].[RoleId]
FROM (
    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[CreationTime], [a].[CreatorUserId], [a].[DeleterUserId], [a].[DeletionTime], [a].[Description], [a].[DisplayName], [a].[IsDefault], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[IsStatic], [a].[LastModificationTime], [a].[LastModifierUserId], [a].[Name], [a].[NormalizedName], [a].[TenantId]
    FROM [AbpRoles] AS [a]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [a].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)) AND (@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [a].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_2)
    ORDER BY [a].[DisplayName]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Id], [a0].[CreationTime], [a0].[CreatorUserId], [a0].[Discriminator], [a0].[IsGranted], [a0].[Name], [a0].[TenantId], [a0].[RoleId]
    FROM [AbpPermissions] AS [a0]
    WHERE [a0].[Discriminator] = N'RolePermissionSetting' AND (@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [a0].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_2)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[RoleId]
ORDER BY [t].[DisplayName], [t].[Id]

    ORDER BY [a].[DisplayName]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[RoleId]

UPDATE [AbpRoles] SET [ConcurrencyStamp] = @p0, [CreationTime] = @p1, [CreatorUserId] = @p2, [DeleterUserId] = @p3, [DeletionTime] = @p4, [Description] = @p5, [DisplayName] = @p6, [IsDefault] = @p7, [IsDeleted] = @p8, [IsStatic] = @p9, [LastModificationTime] = @p10, [LastModifierUserId] = @p11, [Name] = @p12, [NormalizedName] = @p13, [TenantId] = @p14
OUTPUT 1
WHERE [Id] = @p15 AND [ConcurrencyStamp] = @p16;

FROM (
    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[AuthenticationSource], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[CreationTime], [a].[CreatorUserId], [a].[DeleterUserId], [a].[DeletionTime], [a].[EmailAddress], [a].[EmailConfirmationCode], [a].[IsActive], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[IsEmailConfirmed], [a].[IsLockoutEnabled], [a].[IsPhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[IsTwoFactorEnabled], [a].[LastModificationTime], [a].[LastModifierUserId], [a].[LockoutEndDateUtc], [a].[Name], [a].[NormalizedEmailAddress], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[Password], [a].[PasswordResetCode], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[Surname], [a].[TenantId], [a].[UserName]

    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[UserName], [t].[Id]

    ORDER BY [a].[DisplayName]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
